{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "叶开揭开白夫人当年换婴的真相，傅红雪虽痛苦却不再怨恨，仇恨终于被宽恕取代。丁乘风暗中换走丁白云的毒酒，也揭破马空群装中忘忧草之计，叶开以宽恕劝马空群面对罪孽。丁灵琳报告丁灵中离去、路小佳被荆无命带走，荆无命随后现身，因叶开三次出手救人而重新理解李寻欢的刀与兵器价值，认为叶开的刀也应列天下第一。最后叶开承认身世却仍感念叶家养育之恩，丁乘风问清其姓氏，含蓄认可他与丁灵琳的未来。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我本来的确早就该告诉你的，我几次想说出来，却又……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我并不怪你，因为你并没有错……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也不恨你，我已不会再恨任何人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你也没有错，错的是仇恨，仇恨这件事本身就是错的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "他会好的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "他现在就像是个受了重伤的人，但只要他还活着，无论伤口有多么深，都总有一日会好的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "人，有时也像是壁虎一样，就算割断它的尾巴，它还是很快就会再长出一条新的尾巴来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这比喻很好，非常好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这件事你本不想说出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "我本来总觉得说出这件事后，无论对谁都没有好处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但现在你的想法变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "因为我现在已发觉，我们大家为这件事付出的代价都已太多了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以你已将这件事结束？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她若不死，这件事是不是也同样能结束？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "她本来就不必死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "她就算做错了事，也早已付出了她的代价。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "你当然也知道她根本就不会死的，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是的，她不会死也不必死……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "你……你难道……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "我早已知道你为你自己准备了一瓶毒酒，所以……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "所以你就将那瓶毒酒换走了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "我早已将你所有的毒酒都换走了，你就算将那些毒酒全喝下去，最多也只不过大醉一场而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "一个像我这样的老古板，有时也会做一两件狡猾．事的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "我在笑我自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "笑你自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "花白凤都没有死，我为什么一定要死？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "我现在才知道她比我还可怜，她甚至连自己的儿子是谁都不知道，连她都能活得下去，我为什么就活不下去？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "你本来就应该活下去，每个人都应该活下去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "他怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "我喝下的毒酒，若根本不是毒酒，他喝的岂非也……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "你让他喝下去的，也只不过是瓶陈年大曲而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "也许他早已知道你要对付他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "所以他看见我桌上有酒，就立刻故意喝了下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "你当然也应该知道，他本来绝不是个肯随便喝酒的人！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "然后他又故意装出中毒的样子，等着看我要怎样对付他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "你怎么对付他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "我居然告诉了他，那瓶酒是用忘忧草配成的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "text": "他当然知道吃了忘忧草之后，会有什么反应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "丁白云",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "所以他就故意装成这样子，不但骗过了我，也骗过了那些想杀他的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你……你难道连死都不让我死？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我只想问你，你为什么忽然又要死了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我难道连死都不能死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你喝下去的，若真是毒酒，现在还可以活着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "就因为那酒里没有毒，你现在反而要死，这岂非是件很滑稽的事？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你认为那忘忧草既然能令你忘记所有的痛苦和仇恨，别人也就会忘记你的仇恨了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "其实除了忘忧草之外，还有样东西，也同样可以令你忘记那痛苦和仇恨的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "那就是宽恕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "宽恕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "若连你自己都无法宽恕自己，别人又怎么会宽恕你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "但一个人也只有在他已真的能宽恕别人时，才能宽恕他自己，所以你若已真的宽恕别人，别人也同样宽恕了你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "三哥走了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "两个三哥都走了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "两个三哥？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "丁灵中是自己走的，我们想拦住他，可是他一定要走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "路小佳也走了，是被一个人带走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "他没有死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我们本来以为他的伤已无救，可是那人却说他还有法子让他活下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "那个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不认得他，我们本来也不让他把路……路三哥带走的，可是我们根本就没法子阻拦他。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我从来也没见过武功那么高的人，只轻轻挥了挥手，我们就近不了他的身。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "他是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是个独臂人，穿着件很奇怪的黄麻长衫，一双眼睛好像是死灰色的，我也从来没有见过任何人有那种眼睛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "荆无命！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他没有亲人，也没有朋友，一向将路小佳当做他自己的儿子，他既然肯将小佳带走，小佳就绝不会死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他既然来了，应该看看我的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "他绝不会来，因为他知道有个小李探花的弟子在这里。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你难道认为他还没有忘记他和小李探花之间的仇恨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "有些事是永远忘不了的，因为……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "我一直都在这里，只可惜你看不见而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你就是叶开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知道我是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我已有多年未曾见到李寻欢了，我一直都在找他。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我还想找他比一比，究竟是他的刀快，还是我的剑快！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但现在我却已改变了主意，你可知道为了什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是因为你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "因为我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "看见了你，我才知道我是比不上李寻欢的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "路小佳只懂得杀人，可是你……你刚才出手三次，却都是为了救人的命！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道'百晓生'这个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他虽然并不是正直的人，但他的兵器谱却很公正。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "上官金虹虽然死在李寻欢手里，但他的武功，却的确在李寻欢之上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "李寻欢能杀上官金虹，并不是因为他的武功，而是因为他的信心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们交手时，只有我一个人是亲眼看见的，我看得出他的武功，实在不如上官金虹，我一直不懂，他怎么会战胜的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但现在我已了解，一件兵器的真正价值，并不在它的本身，而在于它做的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "李寻欢能杀上官金虹，只因为他并不是为了想杀人而出手的，他做的事，上可无愧于天下，下则无愧于人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "百晓生若也懂得这道理，他就该将李寻欢的刀列为天下第一",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以现在若有人再作兵器谱，就应该将你的刀列为天下第一，因为你刚才做的事，是任何人都做不到的，所以你这柄刀的价值，也绝没有任何兵器能比得上！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你现在当然已不必再隐瞒你的身世。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "但我也不能忘记叶家的养育之恩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "除了你之外，他们也没有别的子女？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "他们没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "所以你还是姓叶？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 507,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "木叶的叶，开朗的开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你一定会奇怪我为什么要问这些话，但我却不能不问个清楚，因为……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "丁乘风",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我只有这么一个女儿，我若要将她交给别人时，至少总不能不知道这个人是姓什么的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    }
